03:49.675 --> 03:52.007
Nothing. Come on.

04:15.382 --> 04:16.757
Hello, Yelena.

04:22.048 --> 04:23.965
What are you doing here?

04:28.465 --> 04:30.175
Frank wrote me.

04:32.383 --> 04:35.173
The letter said he's sick.

04:35.175 --> 04:37.090
You should have called.

04:44.300 --> 04:45.883
This is Willow.

04:47.590 --> 04:48.757
Hi.

05:03.925 --> 05:05.258
Come in.

05:08.175 --> 05:09.675
Okay, come on.

05:43.340 --> 05:47.090
Your husband doesn't mind you
traveling so far alone?

05:51.425 --> 05:52.883
I'm not married.

05:59.425 --> 06:02.215
