the baby here.

06:36.883 --> 06:38.800
How long has he been like this?

06:41.800 --> 06:44.215
He has been sick for many years.

06:46.550 --> 06:47.883
Can I see him?

06:55.590 --> 06:58.632
It is best that we do not
disturb him in the evening.

07:02.800 --> 07:06.923
We should call the taxi
and discuss this tomorrow.

07:06.925 --> 07:07.923
Oh, I...

07:07.925 --> 07:09.923
There is this very nice hotel

07:09.925 --> 07:12.338
in the town.

07:12.340 --> 07:14.423
Let me get my book.

07:47.633 --> 07:52.463
Uh, this is taxi
and, uh, this is the inn.

07:52.465 --> 07:55.675
It's a good place.
The phone in there on table.

08:10.383 --> 08:12.550
I can't get a dial tone.

08:26.050 --> 08:28.008
The weather can cause trouble.

08:29.300 --> 08:31.715
Maybe we could stay here
tonight.

08:33.631 --> 08:35.589
This is not possible.

08:35.591 --> 08:38.716
But the inn is only
a few kilometers away.

08:40.381 --> 08:41.589
Oh, it's freezing outside.

08:41.591 --> 08:44.005
I don't wanna walk her
all night in the cold.

08:44.006 --> 08:47.714
Children are much stronger
than you think, Madeline.

08:47.716 --> 08:49.255
She will be fine.

08:49.257 --> 08:51.380
Don't tell me
she'll be fine, okay?

08:51.382 --> 08:52.589
I don't need parenting advice
from a woman

08:52.591 --> 08:54.508
who abandoned her child.

09:02.675 --> 09:04.382
Repeat, please.

09:09.050 --> 09:11.548
I don't need parenting advice

09:11.550 --> 09:13.507
from a woman
who abandoned her child.

09:20.050 --> 09:23.464
I did not abandon you.

09:23.466 --> 09:26.716
I wanted you
to have a better life!

09:35.300 --> 09:37.380
This conversation
isn't appropriate

09:37.382 --> 09:39.300
in front of the child.

09:50.300 --> 09:51.632
I agree.

09:55.591 --> 09:57.714
- No, sweetie, we have to go.
- Where are we going?

09:57.716 --> 09:59.633
- I don't wanna leave.
- Please.

10:01.257 --> 10:02.715
My apologies.

10:05.132 --> 10:06.925
You should, please, stay.

10:09.007 --> 10:11.757
But there are things I..

10:12.841 --> 10:14.758
...wanted to tell you.

10:16.675 --> 10:18.757
We can discuss this in morning.

10:23.257 --> 10:24.425
Please.

10:36.466 --> 10:37.591
Goodnight.

10:38.507 --> 10:40.048
Goodnight.

10:40.050 --> 10:41.839
Goodnight.

10:41.841 --> 10:44.425
Oh! What this?

10:46.716 --> 10:48.883
- I made this.
- Oh.

10:51.425 --> 10:55.091
I used to make these
with your mother.

10:59.800 --> 11:02.714
Did she ever tell you that?

11:10.466 --> 11:11.800
Goodnight.

11:17.675 --> 11:18.800
Madeline.

11:20.257 --> 11:22.257
Mommy, was this your room?

11:56.132 --> 11:57.632
Yelena?

12:18.425 --> 12:20.757
Madeline.

12:22.132 --> 12:23.425
Madeline.

12:28.550 --> 12:30.882
- You warm?
- Toasty.

12:34.132 --> 12:35.590
Good.

12:39.550 --> 12:42.632
Are you mad or are you sad?

12:45.800 --> 12:47.466
I'm just tired.

12:50.007 --> 12:51.925
You wanna say
your goodnight prayers?

12:56.716 --> 13:00.880
Angels bless and angels keep

13:00.882 --> 13:03.839
angels guard me while I sleep.

13:03.841 --> 13:07.589
Bless my heart
and bless my home

13:07.591 --> 13:10.800
bless my spirit as I roam.

13:19.966 --> 13:22.425
Jesus, we shouldn't be here.

18:38.258 --> 18:40.425
Madeline, are you alright?

18:44.258 --> 18:47.173
Come on, get up. You'll freeze.

18:47.175 --> 18:49.923
Inside! It's cold!

18:49.925 --> 18:51.463
Go!

18:51.465 --> 18:53.382
Why am I out here?

19:21.425 --> 19:23.215
I don't think..

19:24.465 --> 19:26.923
At least
your daughter is here

19:26.925 --> 19:30.965
and family is what
is important now.

19:36.675 --> 19:38.550
Hello, Madeline.

19:42.258 --> 19:44.175
You remember Father Joseph?

19:51.133 --> 19:52.213
That's enough.

19:52.215 --> 19:55.175
You still wear the cross
I gave you.

19:57.383 --> 19:59.050
Uh, I do.

20:00.715 --> 20:04.088
Can I fix you
some breakfast, Madeline?

20:04.090 --> 20:06.881
No, that's okay.
We're gonna have to get going.

20:06.883 --> 20:08.633
Get a room in the town.

20:10.508 --> 20:12.173
Here, you want some cheese.

20:20.508 --> 20:22.050
Finish your food.

20:23.383 --> 20:25.756
Your mother was just
telling me about

20:25.758 --> 20:28.548
