last night.

20:31.215 --> 20:32.925
How are you feeling?

20:38.258 --> 20:39.633
Fine.

20:43.465 --> 20:46.256
I'm very sorry
about your father.

20:46.258 --> 20:47.883
He is, uh..

20:50.965 --> 20:52.673
...a good friend

20:52.675 --> 20:54.381
and was a very gifted priest.

20:54.383 --> 20:56.463
Father Joseph has been coming

20:56.465 --> 20:59.338
for morning prayer with him.

20:59.340 --> 21:04.256
He has been very generous
with his time.

21:04.258 --> 21:06.588
We all must find forgiveness.

21:06.590 --> 21:08.338
Will you join us, Madeline?

21:10.008 --> 21:11.923
