21:11.925 --> 21:14.340
to find peace before he dies.

21:20.050 --> 21:21.338
No.

21:21.340 --> 21:24.923
Um, I think we should
probably get walking.

21:24.925 --> 21:28.713
Walk? I'll drive you into town
on my way back.

21:28.715 --> 21:30.548
I think that's okay.

21:30.550 --> 21:32.923
Mom, you said
I was gonna meet Grandpa.

21:32.925 --> 21:34.173
Come on.

21:34.175 --> 21:35.963
You've come this far, Madeline.

21:35.965 --> 21:38.090
Please join us.

21:39.508 --> 21:42.425
You won't have another chance
to say goodbye.

21:58.425 --> 22:00.965
Frank, Madeline is here..

22:02.883 --> 22:04.633
