Madeline?

23:53.508 --> 23:55.048
What's going on?

23:59.550 --> 24:01.338
Why am I tied down?

24:01.340 --> 24:03.088
Willow? Where's my daughter?

24:03.090 --> 24:06.548
She is downstairs
with your mother.

24:06.550 --> 24:08.300
Why are my hands tied?

24:09.633 --> 24:12.048
Because you lost control.

24:16.840 --> 24:19.215
You did not imagine it.

24:20.840 --> 24:23.175
What the hell
is happening to me?

24:27.258 --> 24:28.466
No.

24:30.590 --> 24:32.840
I believe you have been blessed.

24:36.008 --> 24:38.258
The holy wounds of Stigmata.

24:46.633 --> 24:47.758
I..

24:49.590 --> 24:52.963
I just came here to see my dad.

24:52.965 --> 24:54.175
No.

24:55.465 --> 24:59.756
That is not why you come here.

24:59.758 --> 25:01.506
Let me go! Please, please.

25:01.508 --> 25:03.925
Please, just let me go.
Just let me go.

