I perform mass

25:07.633 --> 25:10.548
for the Sisters
of Mercy Convent.

25:10.550 --> 25:14.758
Pray, Mother Superior
may be able to help you.

25:18.840 --> 25:19.965
Willow!

25:21.175 --> 25:22.383
Willow?

25:23.550 --> 25:25.588
Willow!

25:25.590 --> 25:27.838
Yelena, where is she?

25:27.840 --> 25:29.465
Where is she?

25:39.090 --> 25:41.090
Willow, come here. Come on.

25:45.090 --> 25:46.088
Come...

25:46.090 --> 25:49.631
Madeline, you almost killed her.

25:49.633 --> 25:52.341
I tried to keep this from you.

25:54.133 --> 25:57.548
You are a danger
to your daughter here

25:57.550 --> 26:01.175
but Mercy
is a cloistered convent.

26:02.675 --> 26:05.048
If you want to protect her

26:05.050 --> 26:07.713
you will have to go there.

26:07.715 --> 26:09.465
Trust him, Madeline.

26:10.675 --> 26:12.340
Trust him.

26:20.508 --> 26:21.758
Can I get a hug?

26:24.050 --> 26:26.133
When are you coming back?

26:29.008 --> 26:30.383
Soon.

26:39.133 --> 26:41.841
Madeline, we have to leave.

26:43.425 --> 26:46.298
Hey, you wanna say
our nighttime prayer?

26:46.300 --> 26:47.465
Mm.

26:48.550 --> 26:52.088
Angels bless and angels keep

26:52.090 --> 26:55.548
angels guard me while I sleep.

26:55.550 --> 26:59.088
Bless my heart
and bless my home

26:59.090 --> 27:01.757
bless my spirit as I roam.

27:55.550 --> 27:57.006
I'm not crazy about water.

27:57.008 --> 27:58.216
Tsk.

28:03.883 --> 28:08.548
Consider your fear
and let it go.

28:08.550 --> 28:11.881
There are more dangerous things
than water.

28:11.883 --> 28:13.883
Is that supposed
to make me feel better?

28:16.508 --> 28:17.758
Yes.

