If what you are experiencing
is genuine

30:38.590 --> 30:43.507
then submitting to the spiritual
disciplines of our order..

30:45.050 --> 30:48.923
...will help induce
this great gift.

30:48.925 --> 30:50.838
But I don't want
to bring it back.

30:50.840 --> 30:52.881
I wanna get rid of it.

30:52.883 --> 30:54.425
Once witnessed..

30:55.840 --> 30:57.882
...it can be assessed.

