I'd like to call my daughter.

31:03.008 --> 31:05.425
And I want to help you.

31:12.008 --> 31:15.381
There are certain rules
we all follow.

31:15.383 --> 31:18.506
We are not to leave our rooms
after the evening bell.

31:18.508 --> 31:20.048
We do not wander alone

31:20.050 --> 31:22.506
and we do not speak
without reason to do so.

31:22.508 --> 31:25.713
And we do not go
to the bell tower.

31:25.715 --> 31:27.338
That's the torture chamber.

31:27.340 --> 31:30.088
