32:56.258 --> 32:58.175
I'd like to call my daughter.

33:02.050 --> 33:03.465
Yes.

33:07.633 --> 33:08.966
Welcome to Mercy.

33:12.300 --> 33:14.300
She's an odd girl, isn't she?

33:23.383 --> 33:26.258
I found her in the garden.
She's a refugee.

33:28.090 --> 33:30.465
