Amen.

36:34.341 --> 36:35.550
- Amen.
- Amen.

36:41.758 --> 36:46.008
It's quite normal that others
might feel threatened by you.

36:49.175 --> 36:52.341
What you have is physical.

36:54.675 --> 36:57.214
Tangible evidence

36:57.216 --> 36:59.383
in a world of abstracts.

37:12.383 --> 37:14.425
Envy is a sin.

37:16.550 --> 37:19.133
We are all sinners, aren't we?

37:24.800 --> 37:29.133
Now would you like
to call your daughter?

37:31.133 --> 37:33.050
Let her know you're alright.

37:36.425 --> 37:37.591
Yes.

38:22.508 --> 38:24.381
Hello?

38:24.383 --> 38:25.591
Hello?

38:28.091 --> 38:31.089
What happened
at your parents' house?

38:31.091 --> 38:32.423
There's something wrong
with the phone.

38:32.425 --> 38:34.923
The lines are old.

38:34.925 --> 38:37.298
They get frozen sometimes.

38:37.300 --> 38:39.506
We can try again later.

38:52.550 --> 38:55.466
What happened
at your parents' house?

38:59.341 --> 39:00.925
I don't remember.

39:02.008 --> 39:03.383
Yes, you do.

39:06.341 --> 39:07.883
Sit down.

39:20.508 --> 39:22.050
Loosen your hair.

39:23.841 --> 39:25.216
Why?

39:28.258 --> 39:30.508
I want you to relax.

39:40.425 --> 39:42.175
Close your eyes.

39:45.966 --> 39:48.383
Now clear your mind..

39:51.716 --> 39:54.216
...and breathe.

39:59.633 --> 40:01.506
What do you remember?

40:09.383 --> 40:13.214
I heard noises
coming from the barn.

40:17.008 --> 40:20.006
What noises did you hear?

40:20.008 --> 40:23.423
Hear?

40:23.425 --> 40:25.550
A cat was crying
inside the well.

40:31.800 --> 40:33.131
Go deeper.

40:34.841 --> 40:36.508
Deeper! Deeper!

40:40.716 --> 40:42.466
Come with me.

40:46.633 --> 40:48.466
What do you see?

40:59.550 --> 41:00.841
I'm a child.

41:07.050 --> 41:08.548
Angels bless and angels keep

41:08.550 --> 41:10.339
angels guard me while I sleep.

41:10.341 --> 41:11.798
Bless my heart
and bless my home

41:11.800 --> 41:13.673
bless my spirit as I roam.

41:13.675 --> 41:14.964
Angels guard and angels keep

41:14.966 --> 41:16.798
angels guard me while I sleep.

41:16.800 --> 41:19.381
Bless my heart and bless
my home, bless my spirit..

41:33.675 --> 41:36.300
Bless my spirit, bless
