41:38.716 --> 41:40.006
Help!

41:40.008 --> 41:41.881
No, Madeline.

41:41.883 --> 41:44.508
You need to go back
down the well!

41:49.258 --> 41:51.631
Sit down, Madeline.
We're not finished.

41:51.633 --> 41:54.464
Wha.. What was that?

42:02.091 --> 42:05.631
Stigmatics are blessed
with wounds

42:05.633 --> 42:08.466
as a connection
to the sufferings of Christ.

42:16.758 --> 42:20.214
But I'm afraid
you are experiencing wounds

42:20.216 --> 42:24.714
as a connection
to the sufferings of your life.

42:24.716 --> 42:26.633
What's that supposed to mean?

42:28.925 --> 42:31.633
Old wounds can cause new ones.

42:33.383 --> 42:37.006
There is something dangerous
trapped inside you, Madeline

42:37.008 --> 42:39.589
and we need to drag it out.

42:39.591 --> 42:41.798
We'll try again tomorrow.

