Come on up here.

43:04.050 --> 43:06.758
If you stay in the yard, they'll
end up giving you a broom.

43:14.550 --> 43:16.925
I swear, someday I'm gonna burn
these clothes.

43:19.300 --> 43:22.425
This is pretty much the only
place that we can talk freely.

43:24.675 --> 43:27.675
Plus, it comes
with other benefits.

43:31.008 --> 43:32.300
Mew-mew.

43:35.841 --> 43:37.758
Do you want to hold her?

43:49.883 --> 43:51.175
You okay?

43:53.758 --> 43:55.008
